OL,3,CGreenwich hospice launches appeal for
OL,4,C'once-in-a-generation' renovation
OL,6,FA hospice in Greenwich has launched an
OL,7,Fappeal to raise #400,000 for a "once-
OL,8,Fin-a-generation" renovation.
OL,10,FThe Community Hospice in Abbey Wood
OL,11,Fsupports around 3,000 people living
OL,12,Fwith a life-limiting condition across
OL,13,FGreenwich and Bexley each year, with
OL,14,Falmost 400 people spending time on the
OL,15,Fwards.
OL,17,FBosses want to upgrade the facility's
OL,18,F"outdated" specialist inpatient unit
OL,19,Fso it can better meet the needs of
OL,20,Fpatients.
