OL,3,CGreenwich hospice launches appeal for
OL,4,C'once-in-a-generation' renovation
OL,6,FThe plans would see the hospice
OL,7,Ftransforming their existing shared
OL,8,Fbays into private, ensuite bedrooms,
OL,9,Fwhich they say would give patients and
OL,10,Ffamilies "dignity, privacy and
OL,11,Findependence".
OL,13,FJim Free was a patient at the hospice,
OL,14,Fhaving been admitted following a lung
OL,15,Fcancer diagnosis. He died there on 28
OL,16,FDecember 2019 at the age of 72.
