OL,3,CGreenwich hospice launches appeal for
OL,4,C'once-in-a-generation' renovation
OL,6,FHis widow Sue Free, 77, is backing the
OL,7,Fhospice's Christmas appeal so that
OL,8,Fmore patients can have the privacy and
OL,9,Fsupport that she and her husband
OL,10,Freceived.
OL,12,FShe told ITV News London: "It just
OL,13,Fmakes such a difference when you're
OL,14,Fsitting there seeing the person you've
OL,15,Fbeen married to for over 48 years,
OL,16,Fleaving you, it was really hard.
