OL,3,CGreenwich hospice launches appeal for
OL,4,C'once-in-a-generation' renovation
OL,6,FDeputy chief exectuive Aneta Saunders
OL,7,Fsaid the need to fundraise for the
OL,8,Fproject had become "urgent".
OL,10,F"We had amazing opportunity through a
OL,11,Fgovernment grant and we have been
OL,12,Fbeautifully supported by the Royal
OL,13,FBorough of Greenwich.
OL,15,F"But we need to spend the money this
OL,16,Ffinancial year, so we need to raise
OL,17,Fanother 400,000 by the end of March to
OL,18,Fallow us to complete the works. The
OL,19,Fwork is about to start in April, so we
OL,20,Fneed to finish it in March."
